---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 184
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Obedience
  - 191
By: Ibn 'Atâ’illâh
---
Disobedience which engenders humility and a sense of poverty is better
than obedience which engenders hauteur and a sense of pride.
